casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Wesselman.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Wesselman (1990), 56 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. 90-1947 Submitted November 14, 1990 Decided November 21, 1990.)

The resignation of Edwin Adolph Wesselman as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
